cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.DB, cs.CY 

The paper discusses the development of an online procurement system with a focus on blockchain technology, which involves security and privacy concerns. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves the integration of various web development languages and hosting of the site, which falls under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The development of the system also involves programming logic and testing, which falls under cs.SE (Software Engineering). The system also deals with the storage and retrieval of data, which falls under cs.DB (Databases). Lastly, the paper discusses the privacy concerns of the system, which falls under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
